Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.61,0:00:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冯·布朗号在 第七轨道待命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯大林号 维盖拉号 比尔盖茨号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.97,0:00:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往第二轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八航母群 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.31,0:00:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速3.7点处与布莱斯特号会合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.92,0:00:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四补给班抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.45,0:00:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对预定时间迟到10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.46,0:00:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉升轨道 马格南
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第51战斗群要出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传感器警报 距离500
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.13,0:00:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙色14.233A 大型热源接近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疑似战舰级
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反舰 反机动战士 准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右转舵10 舰首下沉俯角15度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獾阵炮启动 柏瑞安瞄准敌舰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹发射管1-4号装填科林斯飞弹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柏瑞安 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:46.88,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\fs32}（被锁定）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.21,0:00:50.32,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\fs32}（任务失败）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在搞什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.54,0:00:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样初阵就会被击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.31,0:00:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 舰队司令来电
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正练得热火朝天的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.73,0:01:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.75,0:01:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.46,0:01:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是 国防产业联合理事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩尔达·阿兹拉尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.79,0:01:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该听说过他的尊姓大名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.80,0:01:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他此次登舰	
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.51,0:01:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是作为观察员 协助运用新型机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.91,0:01:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供现场指导
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好配合他的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.46,0:01:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照 舰长小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.43,0:01:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！在下娜塔尔·巴基露露少校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没想到 我们船上的舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是位如此年轻美貌的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.12,0:01:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有意安排的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.35,0:01:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她非常优秀 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是军人世家出身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.62,0:02:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 被调来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾在那艘大天使号上担任大副
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.97,0:02:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？那可来头不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们此行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是去击沉那艘大天使号的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:03.11,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}拦路者
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.49,0:04:03.11,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord2\shad0\1a&HFF&\3a&H00&\an3\fs60}拦路者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是根据雅金·多维资料预测出的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒号可能选择的航线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是L4的殖民卫星群？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真伤脑筋啊 那块地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会被神秘团伙当作老巢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会又被这样利用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莱茵派虽不成大气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但或许是厌战情绪作怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队内部各自为战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现什么状况也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾见过巴尔菲鲁特将军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在难以想像他竟然会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个油嘴滑舌的花花公子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉议长也被他的名声所骗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且他还是奇迹般生还的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉命去给这位英雄擦屁股的可是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 有什么办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万事不可能像想像得那么顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何况是人心中的真实想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓人心隔肚皮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的阿斯兰已经是敌人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下得了手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 那个叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很累吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是血肉之躯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个战场到另一个战场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始终是这样的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 身为军人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许理所应当
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们也并非
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生就是个军人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望早点结束啊 这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此我得到了终极钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:06:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在这里它无法打开大门
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想早日打开那扇门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没记错的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座卫星开战前发生过生化危机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被下令遗弃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曼德尔的事故 我也记得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时闹得沸沸扬扬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好在 因此设施都保存完整
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 用来安营扎寨再合适不过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前的问题还是月球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说现在地球军 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正从夺回的维多利亚港
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陆续将部队运往那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是打算对PLANT发动总攻吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟有这想法的人不在少数
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了蓝色而纯净的世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 的确是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么剿灭调整人世界就能蓝色而纯净了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底 到底什么是蓝色而纯净？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在PLANT看来 这理由简直莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 PLANT上也把自然人看成是累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头头们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不会被动挨打 会主动反击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打到自然人不再有还手之力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲的时代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 解铃还须系铃人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在每个战乱的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有许多我们这样想法的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想开创一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同于现在的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原来在这儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你 脑袋没退化成小白鼠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人闷头多想也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家才把想法说出来不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候别一个人呆着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很疼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被父亲打
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…没能阻止父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才知道自己的无能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一无所能 一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…大家都差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自以为知道才有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和父亲的事 别这么早就放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有机会 见面再好好谈下不就是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以别在这种地方一个人闷闷不乐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…你？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那个…我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库洛德·布卢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强化植入平台3
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-370的生体CPU
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个人资料被全部删除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥卢加·萨布纳克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-131生体CPU
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,植入平台2
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有个人资料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏尼·安德拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,植入平台4
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-252生体CPU
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有个人资料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人都不是驾驶员而是装备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被当作消耗品 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离L4还有多远？现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:10:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在下仍无法赞同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…在毫无依据的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往L4…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的情报非常可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是依据 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能说毫无依据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 情报来自PLANT
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由和正义 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是它们的代号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三艘纳斯卡级为执行相关的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正朝L4去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真那样不就完了吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 听我说一句
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确实是指挥这艘船的舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 还有人站在更高的角度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从全局上考虑指挥着这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要你好好配合我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好不要随便忘记长官的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞得下的弹药和物资都带上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后的补给渠道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有留在PLANT上的同志们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.05,0:11:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想方设法接济
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船还要多久可以完成最终调试？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 请尽快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起啊 粉红头发的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校！这种事让我们来做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 这也是训练的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也做过宇宙模拟训练吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总不能老让孩子们打头阵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒号既然是专用舰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由和正义去那里比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有强袭和暴风
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我和阿斯兰这就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民卫星曼德尔港内
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现三艘舰船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认其中一艘为大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们抢先一步 真是LUCKLY
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 让我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船击沉不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要那两架机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们准备出击 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天得给我好好干
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰准备进入战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獾阵炮 柏瑞安启动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹发射管 全部装填蛮锤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗恩格林瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标 大天使级一号舰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现大型热源接近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.63,0:13:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疑似战舰级物体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离700 橙色11.18A
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对照资料库 无
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 一级战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 一级战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 全员 一级战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗恩格林2号 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号出击 去港外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉米亚斯舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草雉的情况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法出动 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒号还未完成最终调试
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:14:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 那么请在港内待命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探明敌人是扎夫特还是联合军
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就知道他们的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獾阵炮 柏瑞安启动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰尾导弹发射管 全门装填
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定能成为位好舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能再见 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战场以外的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是地球联合军 宇宙战舰主天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号 请回话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰要求贵舰立即无条件投降
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受作为叛逃舰的处分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜塔尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴基露露中尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如不服从的话 将击沉贵舰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 这是敌舰的光学影像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同型号舰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 拉米亚斯舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:14:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.26,0:15:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以这样的方式见面 深感遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在阿拉斯加的遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有所耳闻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 请先投降
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与军队上层再做商议
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会尽力为你们辩护
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰的性能 你应该了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜塔尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是阿拉斯加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们 对地球军本身产生了疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 不会降服或服退
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉米亚斯舰长…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 还以为你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着让人笑掉大牙 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说就能说通 这世上也不会有争端了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.31,0:15:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为无法理解所以才会变成敌人不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敌人就必须干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿兹拉尔理事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灾祸 禁断 劫掠出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.61,0:16:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不沉舰大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你们该沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿兹拉尔是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色宇宙的盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路线清空 131出击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主天使号上机动战士出击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 穆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.68,0:16:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰·萨拉 正义出动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴风 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴风 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴风和强袭负责掩护大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰 是那三架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心残骸 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是那些高分子化合纤维
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.13,0:16:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出港后最大战速 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号左舷就位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么活捉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一半也行？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号及不明舰只1
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航线绿色94.3B
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹发射管1-6号
