Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎最大功率
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝那种不着边际的方向放导弹做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂就请别说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来看看水平有没有见涨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人只有一艘 瞄准引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 有绳索缠住了船体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉断它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅葱 有东西缠住了船体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去清除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 作死的节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草雉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 夏尼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 那个死鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看什么 快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 谁来告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么戏提前开场了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除主天使号外还有两艘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.73,0:19:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一艘是长腿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军好像只派来一艘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管几艘 这么混乱的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无从下手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和伊扎克从卫星内部潜入
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先收集情况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长您亲自去？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荷尔德林号和赫伊津哈号按兵不动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民卫星曼德尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺利的话可以让许多事就此了结
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主天使号呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.37,0:20:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残骸很多…
