Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来不及
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.19,0:20:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的战术
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不值得得到您的夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜塔尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕获那架机体就可以了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么呼叫灾祸和劫掠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柏瑞安 戈特弗里德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准 敌机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次你是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 自由…
