Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.61,0:21:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这感觉 难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 喂！大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.11,0:21:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有扎夫特
